  "markdown_content": "\n## Executive Summary\n\nUser frustrated by repeated browser extension popup interrupting workflow on iOS Manus app. Cannot install desktop extension from mobile, seeking automatic browser selection or flow optimization. Agent explains technical limitations and provides workaround solutions.\n\n\n## Context & Intent\n\nUser experiencing workflow interruptions due to Manus browser extension popup on iOS, seeking ways to streamline the process and eliminate confirmation prompts\n\n\n## What Was Done\n\nAnalyzed the technical issue, identified that the popup is generated by Manus system (not controllable by agent), and provided clear options and workarounds\n\n\n## Outputs Produced\n\n- [analysis] technical issue diagnosis — Identified browser extension popup as system-generated behavior\n- [solution table] options comparison — Table comparing different approaches with realistic outcomes\n\n## Key Decisions & Validations\n\n- Clarified that browser extension popup is system-generated, not agent-controlled\n- Recommended clicking 'No, use default browser' as immediate workaround\n- Offered to avoid browser-dependent tasks when possible\n\n## Lessons Learned\n\nWorked well:\n\n- Direct technical explanation without deflection\n- Clear options table format\nFailed / suboptimal:\n\n- Initial response lacked context about incomplete user message\nDiscoveries:\n\n- User workflow heavily impacted by system UI interruptions on mobile\n\n## Challenges & Blockers\n\n- Cannot control Manus system popup behavior\n- No automatic timeout for browser extension confirmation\n- Platform limitation between iOS and desktop functionality\n\n## Open Questions\n\n- What was the original task that triggered the browser extension popup?\n- Can future tasks be designed to avoid browser dependencies?\n\n## Next Steps\n\n- User to click 'No, use default browser' when popup appears\n- Prioritize non-browser tasks to reduce interruptions\n- Identify and relaunch the original blocked task\n---\nUID: jHeC4WPRLQMcHBF2wx96YA | Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514 | Cost: $0.0147\n"
